
Running Nginx & Nginx Plus as a container on RHEL8 with Podman 

RHEL8 is an intelligent OS design by Redhat for running modern workloads in Hybrid environment. It is higly consitent and
comptable with various third party softwares, hardwares and prominent public and private cloud providers today and loaded up with some fabulous features
like built in mangement, predictive analysis which differentiate it from other enterpise grade OS.
 
The default container engine for RHEL8 OS family is the "Podman". It is expecinally seecure, efficent and deamonless container engine for deploying 
containerised applications.



